	+ commit 738ab548f13cc032f01ca5da1f8dc3ea221b209d


2017-11-16  Damien Goutte-Gattat  <dgouttegattat@incenp.org>

	fltk: Fix compilation and distcheck errors.
	+ commit 89ae5378d1cc54be0825bcfa3ea567b1caa4a247
